      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Huh… you’re already ready? You really are impatient… Don’t rush so much! Alright then~ this time, can you take down #r#o14#s and #o32#s#k and bring me #b30 #t4000014#s and #t4000028#s#k? I’m counting on you!"
